thread.title: Kenya central bank holds benchmark lending rate at 11.50 pct
thread.title_full: Kenya central bank holds benchmark lending rate at 11.50 pct | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: Kenya central bank holds benchmark lending rate at 11.50 pct
text:
NAIROBI, Sept 22 Kenya's central bank held its benchmark lending rate at 11.50 percent on Tuesday, its Monetary Policy Committee said, in line with the market's expectations.
The committee said in a statement the measures it had taken in previous sittings had helped lower inflation towards its medium target of 5 percent. (Reporting by Duncan Miriri ; Editing by Angus MacSwan )
